    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the creamed coconut is cool, add your <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>dried thyme</strong> and <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>to the dissolved creamed coconut</p><p>Add your <strong>diced chicken thigh </strong>to the bowl with your <strong>corn flour </strong>and 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside to marinate for 10 min</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
