      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Jamaican-style curry fried chicken </strong>with the <strong>chips</strong>, <strong>greens </strong>and <strong>jerk-spiced gravy</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining sliced chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
